<br>
IC: <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>&quot;...Very well.  We had every intention of allowing you first strike but since you seem so enthusiastic about losing parts of yourself...&quot;</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
Merenth hisses acidly.  Literally.  Deep blue liquid drips from her jaws to the ground, corroding it.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>&quot;You really are ignorant, aren't you?  Taunting the ruby-wing queen.  We were enhanced by a Dark Lord and granted more power than you could ever hold.  We were the one who blew up most of his fortress.&quot;</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
With that, she spits a stream of her acid into Thrain's eye and screeches.  Instantly her clan lands in precise files and snarls at him before they all smash him simultaneously with fireballs.  The smoke clears with the wind from their wings as they take off again, awaiting the next order. Kaelia is found to have the mage under her claws.<br>
<br>
&quot;What shall I tear off first, Mistress?  An arm, perha-&quot;<br>
<br>
She is flung off of him with a blast of magic but gets up again almost immediately.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>&quot;<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>No one</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> attacks our pet and gets away with it.  When we're done with you there will be nothing left but pieces of your skull lodged in our claw.  This claw!&quot;</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
She brandishes her right foreclaw, which starts to glow with ancient magic.  White bits between the scales, now identified to be fragments of human skulls, seem to enhance it.  Her wings begin to glow as well.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>&quot;We shall test the death-spells ourself!  Flee or be flayed, Thrain!  You look confident but inside you tremble.&quot;</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE HR START--><hr /><!--EZCODE HR END--><br>
