<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:skyblue;">&quot;Even if I was never caught by Hunters, this is practice.  Think of it as a punishment for being so much like the one who caused my queen so much suffering.&quot;</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
