<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>&quot;It was true... I saw it...&quot;</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
*She mutters, under her breath. Then a bit more blood splatters onto her from above and she seems to wake up. Flicking some of it off in disgust-*<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>*I don't want his blood on me anymore*</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
*-she walks quietly over to Iris, using a wide arc around where Thrain was slaughtered. Her dragon senses tell her Iris is slightly upset... Kyla's voice is thick and strange:*<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>&quot;You know, it was going to happen Iris, no matter what we did. I just carried the message. Maby that's why this place feels so wrong -it was always going to happen.&quot;</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
*Then something seems to occur to her, and she asks hurridly*<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>&quot;You did see it too, right?! You saw him go?! Not the body -him?!&quot;</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
*The strangest thing is, it's obviously not the kill that's bothering her -Kyla's seen plenty of those.* <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>~The stars shine only in darkness~ </em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bdragonise.showUserPublicProfile?gid=sugarbird7>Sugarbird7</A> at: 7/24/03 2:45 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=663399><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bdragonise.showUserPublicProfile?gid=lythiaren>Lythiaren</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://images.neopets.com/smileys/eyrie.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle><font Color=red>~Admin Dragon!~<br>
~Merenth, the Ruby-winged golden queen!~</font>
</span><br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(7/24/03 8:44 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fdragonisefrm17.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3.topic&index=197>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://images.neopets.com/pets/80by80/eyrie_blue_happy.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: *Back from a battle*</span><hr size=1> Merenth flicks her wings at the dragons overhead and they all disappear.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>&quot;They were making this place too crowded now.  My brother left.  His spell wore off.  Need me anymore?  Or should I get back to my den?  A flaying-spell, variation or not, hurts the caster.&quot;</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
Before either of them could answer she calls rain to wash off the blood.  Once Kaelia is clean she hovers over Merenth's head and changes back, coiling around the queen's horn.  Merenth shows off her claw, with all Thrain's blood cleaned off, which is slowly bleeding from a long gash across it.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>&quot;This is what happens when I use it.  It's how I pull energy from the one I kill, so I can use the same spell again right away if I need it.  And Iris, if you don't want to be a dragon anymore Kaelia can change you back.  Unless you want to wait and change back yourself?&quot;</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
